Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:03.16,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}scratch it, paint it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:05.91,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}one in the same
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.10,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We couldn't find them
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:11.78,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}we tried to hide them
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:17.38,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)}Words that we couldn't say
