Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.25,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}fools on parade
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:26.57,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}taint it, own it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.05,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}chase it away
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:32.36,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We couldn't make them
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.36,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}we had to break them
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:43.38,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)}Words that we couldn't say
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收获怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己抓去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于那个代号朱丽娅的男人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是真名叫库廉的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这货是个越狱犯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悬赏金可不少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是抓住了这家伙 我就让你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在你上面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到离天空最近的大楼顶上来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人会把东西交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无妨 我也想见见你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞坏了BEBOP 却留下了剑鱼和榔头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(1246.934,980)}Sword Fish
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(1548.267,980)}Hammer Head
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是让我们来找你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自作多情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在试探我们么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保险箱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面只有两万块耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就装吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 朱丽娅是什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好像是和斯派克有点关系的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/-------------- Part B --------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物 礼物 还没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等级EX+ 是真货
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要的土卫六蛋白石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我向库廉问声好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那时曾从蝎子爪下救过我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后却出卖了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库廉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以给我那个八音盒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为觉得我不会拆开来调查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到通讯机了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朱丽娅找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她听说是你给我的 就发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又想杀我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我的战友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是我的同志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾一起在沙漠的战场上战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我很崇拜你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么是值得信任的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有必要信任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比夏斯大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世上 没什么值得相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比夏斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是为了保护你这种人而丢掉性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那林也太可怜了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他保护的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是规矩！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱丽娅在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去哪了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤到了内脏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方救护车会不会来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再让我坐上飞行舱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去土卫六
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这身体怎么可能撑得住！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太花时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也活不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在路上也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再回那里一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕能离得近一点也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是斯派克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱丽娅总是提起你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说 你两只眼睛的颜色不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说只要和你对视 心情就会变得很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她总会在你不经意间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐到吧台的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都点同一支曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是微笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去有些悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有收获吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧给我进来 要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱丽娅…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人的自言自语而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有爱德不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过阵子就会告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 算了 无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有星星掉下来了 布尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并非普通的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战士的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是战士？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这星球的某处 战斗到最后一刻的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信伟大意志的可悲灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(889.6,980)}Great Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/-------------- Next --------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.32,0:24:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生往前一寸就是黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.17,0:24:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界真是乱套了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.56,0:24:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 就将我这不走寻常路的脱轨人生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.36,0:24:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给这样的你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.21,0:24:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷幻的狂想曲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.31,0:24:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.36,0:24:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波希米亚狂想曲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.36,0:24:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(960,980)}Bohemian Rhapsody
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.06,0:24:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 你要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.25,0:24:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也来一起浪费人生呢？



